Package com.camerontec.util.datamodel.message

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FieldAllocator
    Interface to be implemented by classes capable of providing FieldProxy and FieldGroupProxy objects.
    MessageContextResources
    Aggregation interface for all MessageContext resources.
    MessageContextResourcesFactory
    Interface for creating MessageContext instances.
    PooledMessageFactoryMXBean
    MXBean interface for PooledMessageFactory instances.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFieldAllocator
    FieldAllocator base class.
    AnyFieldValue
    Field implementation capable of containing a value of any of the supported types.
    IndexedArrayOfFields
    Interface representing an indexed collection of fields and implied field groups.
    MessageContextImpl
    Default MessageContext implementation.
    MessageFactoryProperties
    Class encapsulating message (and related) factory sizing properties and default values.
    MessageImpl
    Concrete Message implementation.
    PooledFieldAllocator
    Pooled FieldAllocator implementation.
    PooledMessageContextResources
    Pooled MessageContextResources implementation.
    PooledMessageFactory<T extends Message>
    A message context which provides access to a set of pooled messages and associated pooled message resources.
    ReadOnlyByteVectorFieldValue
    Field implementation supporting nested structure, but with limited type conversion abilities.
    UnpooledFieldAllocator
    Unpooled FieldAllocator implementation.
    UnpooledMessageContextResources
    Unpooled implementation of MessageContextResources.
    UnpooledMessageFactory<T extends Message>
    Unpooled MessageFactory implementation which creates a new Message on invocation of UnpooledMessageFactory.newMessage().
